00228 /**
00229  * Bit description of the COP0 counter control register
00230  */
00231 typedef union cvmx_core_perf_control {
00232     uint32_t u32;
00233     struct {
00234 #ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN_BITFIELD
00235         uint32_t m:1;        /**< Set to 1 for sel 0 and 0 for sel 2, indicating there are two performance counters */
00236         uint32_t w:1;        /**< Set to 1 indicating counters are 64 bit */
00237         uint32_t reserved_25_29:5;
00238         uint32_t ec:2;       /**< Event Class
00239                       0x0 = root events counted; active in root context
00240                       0x1 = root intervention events counted; active in root context
00241                       0x2 = guest events counted; active in guest context
00242                       0x3 = guest events plus root intervention events counted; active in guest
00243 context */
00244         uint32_t reserved_15_22:8;
00245         cvmx_core_perf_t event:10;
00246                      /**< Selects the event to be counted by the corresponding Counter Register */
00247         uint32_t ie:1;
00248                      /**< Interrupt Enable */
00249         uint32_t u:1;        /**< Count in user mode */
00250         uint32_t s:1;        /**< Count in supervisor mode */
00251         uint32_t k:1;        /**< Count in kernel mode */
00252         uint32_t ex:1;
00253                      /**< Count in exception context */
00254 #else
00255         uint32_t ex:1;
00256         uint32_t k:1;
00257         uint32_t s:1;
00258         uint32_t u:1;
00259         uint32_t ie:1;
00260         uint32_t event:10;
00261         uint32_t reserved_15_22:8;
00262         uint32_t ec:2;
00263         uint32_t reserved_25_29:5;
00264         uint32_t w:1;
00265         uint32_t m:1;
00266 #endif
00267     } s;
00268 } cvmx_core_perf_control_t;

00287 /**
00288  * Return number of TLB entries.
00289  */
00290 static inline int cvmx_core_get_tlb_entries(void)
00291 {
00292     if (OCTEON_IS_MODEL(OCTEON_CN3XXX))
00293         return 32;
00294     else if (OCTEON_IS_MODEL(OCTEON_CN5XXX))
00295         return 64;
00296     else if (OCTEON_IS_OCTEON2())
00297         return 128;
00298     else
00299         return 256;
00300 }
